overview.en: Fontcoin is an open platform for business and entertainment applications that focuses on building the first public chain combining industry, finance and chain to thoroughly solve the performance of the underlying public chain, improve efficiency and experience, and support high-frequency transactions.
overview.zh: Fontcoin 是全球专注打造产、融、链相结合的第一公链彻底解决底层公链的性能，提升效率和体验，支撑高频交易的商业娱乐应用开放平台。
